P A S S G E N
=============

Passgen is interactive easy to use text mode utility for generating passwords and any
other character sequences in a wide range.

It allows you:
	- Set the number of generated passwords;
	- Set the number of characters in the one password;
	- Select the only characters you need;
	- Optionally set the first character as a digit or a letter or a special character;
	- Save the output data to a file or display it on the screen;
	
Passgen is free of any licensing, which means you can use it and its source code for any
purpose, anywhere, anytime.
